      "role": "user",
      "content": "the breathing exercises arent really doing much though. the nausea is making me feel like i might throw up and it's making me even more panicky. honestly it feels more physical than just a \"bad mood\" or whatever. do you think it's actually possible for anxiety to make your chest feel that heavy and make you feel sick to your stomach? i'm just scared it might be something else but i don't want to make a big deal out of nothing if it's just my nerves.",
